IDeployResolution, java.lang.Comparable
public class DeploySetAttributeResolution
extends DeployResolution

A generic resolution for setting the value of a DeployModelObject attribute.

Supports both EStructuralFeature as well as ExtendedAttribute attributes.

Should only be used when a IDeployAttributeValueStatus is not available. A generic resolution for IDeployAttributeValueStatus exists in DeployAttributeValueResolution.

Construct a resolution that will set the attribute of the DeployModelObject of the IDeployStatus.

The object is identified using IDeployResolutionContext.getDeployStatus() and then IDeployStatus.getDeployObject().

Parameters:
context - the deploy resolution context.
generator - the generator creating this status.
attributeName - the name of the status deploy object attribute (EAttribute or ExtendedAttribute).
value - the value to which the attribute will be set.
description - the description of the resoluton.
